{"tid":2292322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國示威升溫 總理下令警方鎮壓 民眾無懼持續上街","createTime":"2020-11-19T11:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T13:40:04.000Z","uid":337052,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e19922d91e357a6a4a6e138a322710b9c586e80","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:46:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">泰國示威升溫 總理下令警方鎮壓</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/11/19 18:15<br />\n<br />\n（中央社曼谷19日綜合外電報導）<span class=\"red\">泰國總理帕拉育（Prayut Chan-o-cha）今天下令安全機構鎮壓抗議人士。警方數天前才在曼谷的示威現場，以強力水柱和催淚瓦斯驅離抗議群眾。</span><br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，泰<span class=\"red\">國自7月以來全國掀起學運浪潮，要求修憲，並且前所未有地呼籲改革不可撼動的王室，以及要求總理帕拉育下台。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">示威人士17日遊行至國會前，與挺王室的保皇派群眾（黃衫軍）爆發學運以來最嚴重衝突，至少6人遭槍擊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">昨天約2萬人聚集在曼谷主要購物區，遊行前往附近的皇家警察總部（Thai Royal Police Headquarters），對警察總部大門的標誌潑漆並在警察總部前大馬路塗鴉。</span><br />\n<br />\n2014年發動政變上台的帕拉育今天發布聲明，警告示威者將會受到法律全面制裁。<br />\n<br />\n帕拉育說：「情勢目前還沒往任何好的方向解決，可能演變成更多衝突、導致更多暴力。」<br />\n<br />\n他又說：「如果這樣下去&hellip;可能破壞國家和最受尊崇的制度。」他指的是君主政體。<br />\n<br />\n帕拉育表示，政府和安全機構必須「加強作為」和徹底執法。<br />\n<br />\n這可能意味更多人將會被當局依嚴厲的冒犯君主罪起訴，任何對王室的批評都可能構成犯罪，包括在社群媒體張貼或分享內容在內。（譯者：陳怡君/核稿：劉學源）1091119<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011190293.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202011190293.aspx&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=4012b1ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011190293.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"133ca8ce6316a79c269f47385d96f7233fdd8378","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wbtrJoHxDHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwbtrJoHxDHE&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=526e187f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wbtrJoHxDHE</a><br />\n民眾無懼持續上街<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FreeYOUTHth/status/1329303576699658241?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFreeYOUTHth%2Fstatus%2F1329303576699658241%3Fs%3D20&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=eb2b3f5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFreeYOUTHth%2Fstatus%2F1329303576699658241%3Fs%3D20&h=84cb5fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FreeYOUTHth/status/1329303576699658241?s=20</a><br />\n這是對全民宣戰嗎"},{"pid":"36aaaa7a8d411a4595d0af9fc72897573f5627f4","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">集會規模日趨升級 泰總理公告：將嚴格依法執法</span></strong><br />\n2020年11月19日 - by hushjoker<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%81-%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%94%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%82%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%94-735x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E0%25B8%2599%25E0%25B8%25B2%25E0%25B8%25A2%25E0%25B8%2581-%25E0%25B9%2580%25E0%25B8%2594%25E0%25B9%2587%25E0%25B8%2594%25E0%25B8%2582%25E0%25B8%25B2%25E0%25B8%2594-735x400.jpg&h=c2527452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊 據泰媒報導 11月19日，泰國總理兼國防部長巴育上將發布總理公告：<br />\n<br />\n對於過去這段時間內的集會形勢，政府及各方一直都在堅持符合法律框架、以國王為國家元首的民主體制的前提下，一同尋求和平解決出路。<br />\n<br />\n儘管政府一直都在展現出解決問題的真心誠意，但形勢並未有緩和趨勢。安全部門在盡全力按照職責維護和平穩定秩序，同時密切關注、評估形勢，在維護國家統一、團結和諧的準則下，按照國際標準謹慎執行，以維護國家及大部分民眾的利益為重。<br />\n<br />\n目前局勢仍未有好轉趨勢，且還有向衝突、嚴重性升級的發展苗頭，如若繼續放任下去，或將對國家、體制、人民財產和生命安全造成損害。<br />\n<br />\n因此，政府和安全部門有必要提升執行水平，嚴格按照現有的所有法律條文規定，對違法的集會人員、置他人自由權利不顧的人士，按照國際通用標準、國家司法程序對上述人員執行案件程序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo_2020-11-19_11-37-34-835x1080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fphoto_2020-11-19_11-37-34-835x1080.jpg&h=394f6507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以此公告。 （編譯：hush 來源：Khaosod）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e8%a7%84%e6%a8%a1%e6%97%a5%e8%b6%8b%e5%8d%87%e7%ba%a7-%e6%b3%b0%e6%80%bb%e7%90%86%e5%85%ac%e5%91%8a%ef%bc%9a%e5%b0%86%e4%b8%a5%e6%a0%bc%e4%be%9d%e6%b3%95%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2F%25e9%259b%2586%25e4%25bc%259a%25e8%25a7%2584%25e6%25a8%25a1%25e6%2597%25a5%25e8%25b6%258b%25e5%258d%2587%25e7%25ba%25a7-%25e6%25b3%25b0%25e6%2580%25bb%25e7%2590%2586%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%2591%258a%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25b0%2586%25e4%25b8%25a5%25e6%25a0%25bc%25e4%25be%259d%25e6%25b3%2595%25e6%2589%25a7%25e6%25b3%2595%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=9f618c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e8%a7%84%e6%a8%a1%e6%97%a5%e8%b6%8b%e5%8d%87%e7%ba%a7-%e6%b3%b0%e6%80%bb%e7%90%86%e5%85%ac%e5%91%8a%ef%bc%9a%e5%b0%86%e4%b8%a5%e6%a0%bc%e4%be%9d%e6%b3%95%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95/</a>"},{"pid":"998b6ac74acaa26488a37c9d23528fd9a0cc9188","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20201118195739-735x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587_20201118195739-735x400.jpg&h=e2866fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國警察總署被示威者包圍並潑顏料！現場還來了一大波鴨子&hellip;<br />\n2020年11月18日 - by lukelai"},{"pid":"43392caea9dc7090b51fa1305234cac5b670cda8","tid":2292322,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"支那係背後教緊佢"},{"pid":"89f63aad471b63489b09e197d6ac8c6939349f14","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">泰國示威竟湧大批黃鴨！真正用途曝光</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n三立新聞網<br />\n2020年11月19日 週四 下午5:25 [GMT+8]&middot;3 分鐘 (閱讀時間)<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n泰國自7月以來反政府示威不斷，且在17日晚間爆發嚴重衝突，再度引起國際關注。更吸睛的是，泰國抗議現場竟然出現大量大型充氣「黃色小鴨」，似乎有些格格不入，<span class=\"red\">原來這些「小鴨兵團」是泰國學生為了「水陸兩路包圍國會」準備的示威道具，不料，「小鴨兵團」還沒下水就被警察水砲車鎮壓，瞬間變成對抗鎮暴警察的「肉身盾牌」、抵擋高壓水砲，意外成為此次抗議的吉祥物之一</span>，引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SDqwXAOL2sgu1kA1_RUMAw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1MC40/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/tuuQttwRxzv3C7MnzKEwew--~B/aD01NDI7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/d814d39133734396d537ae315022be1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSDqwXAOL2sgu1kA1_RUMAw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1MC40%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtuuQttwRxzv3C7MnzKEwew--~B%2FaD01NDI7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fd814d39133734396d537ae315022be1a&h=5e7113ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國示威湧現大批黃色小鴨，備受討論。（圖／翻攝自OldMan_b1推特）<br />\n<br />\n泰國國會17日展開為期兩天的修憲草案辯論，大批反政府示威者聚集在國會大樓外抗議，要求國會採納民間版本的的修憲草案。<span class=\"red\">這次不僅警方派出鎮暴警察、催淚彈與藍色水砲車強力鎮壓，保皇黨的「黃衫軍」示威者也紛紛上街，與反政府示威者爆發嚴重衝突，至少造成55人受傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，抗議群眾也不甘示弱，帶著大批「黃色小鴨」造型的充氣橡皮艇上街，根據泰國網友上傳推特的照片顯示，許多小鴨的「肉身」被拿來擋在抗爭前線，化身盾牌對抗警方的藍色高壓水砲，不少小鴨也因此洩氣陣亡，同時被泰國網友大讚身負「戰功」，意外成為這次抗議的吉祥物，引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DzWuIHxiTI1dzOUCyHEzWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NC42NzA0ODcxMDYwMTcy/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/9e630c74b42a8bd73797e774789f5db4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDzWuIHxiTI1dzOUCyHEzWA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NC42NzA0ODcxMDYwMTcy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F9e630c74b42a8bd73797e774789f5db4&h=fa68e7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃色小鴨被當作盾牌抵抗強力水柱。（圖／翻攝自badiucao推特）<br />\n<br />\n許多人好奇為何會出現這批「黃色小鴨」軍團？事實上，這批小鴨原本是抗議群眾為了「水陸兩路包圍國會」準備的示威道具，示威者原本預計繞過國會正門，「划著小鴨艇」從曼谷的昭披耶河上，水路包抄到國會後門，完成靜坐示威。不料，這批「學運水軍」還沒能入河下水，就直接被陸上警察水砲車鎮壓，因此黃色小鴨才會變成「對抗鎮暴警察」的防守道具，成為轟動國際的抗議象徵。<br />\n<br />\n泰國國會在18日下午泰國國會表決修憲草案，否決公民團體提出的版本，示威者因此表示將於25日再度上街抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fYmLJmoAPxZgkONIdx1qig--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxNS4y/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/b810941735f38c6919ac430ca403d408\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfYmLJmoAPxZgkONIdx1qig--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxNS4y%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fb810941735f38c6919ac430ca403d408&h=40b02939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃色小鴨成為泰國反政府示威象徵。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%AB%9F%E6%B9%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E9%BB%83%E9%B4%A8-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-092528431.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%25B9%25A7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%25B4%25A8-%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2580%2594%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-092528431.html&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=bbabed88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%AB%9F%E6%B9%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E9%BB%83%E9%B4%A8-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-092528431.html</a>"},{"pid":"982466b2dd360b427ea9897e41e9bf0098d40b3e","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EnHJGdjW4AIA2Rt?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEnHJGdjW4AIA2Rt%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=132c290b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EnHJGdrW4AAEqci?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEnHJGdrW4AAEqci%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=7cf8d1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EnHJGdrXEAA3twh?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEnHJGdrXEAA3twh%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=6dde04d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察總部遭潑漆"},{"pid":"2f4873a7015ea056da08e3f4a8621779fa744cf1","tid":2292322,"uid":103521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:59:59.000Z","msg":"黃色係革命色"},{"pid":"110713218b28a4184b6c9558209d671c1601051b","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/18/phpxmquMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2FphpxmquMq.jpg&h=fdd4d1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/18/php5008fl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2Fphp5008fl.jpg&h=3e390934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有泰國繪製「小鴨戰士」，表揚小鴨們被打得千瘡百孔也義無反顧，仍英勇挺立在衝突前線保護學生與市民。（圖擷取自臉書＿ผู้ชายใส่แว่น）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/18/phpyfmexH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2FphpyfmexH.jpg&h=2cb6b61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有泰國網友感念小鴨們在運動中肉身護衛示威者的鞠躬盡瘁，製作小鴨的錶金框遺像，並為小鴨別上勳章，作為戰功的表彰。（圖擷取自推特＿+&alpha;у&alpha;мє+|||）"},{"pid":"080467885bbab4ae71569c5c548c87f0f56b0e8f","tid":2292322,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"